Hey! We're working hard to add people to Gotrade as fast as we can, but right now you need an invite token to sign up. Anyone can get one by joining the waitlist, or by asking an existing user for one.



We really appreciate your patience and can't wait to welcome you. Thank you!


***

ABOUT GOTRADE

Gotrade is a mobile app which allows users from over 150 countries to invest in fractions of US stocks from just $1 allowing users to own $10 of Apple, $5 of Netflix or even $1 of Amazon. Accounts are insured by the SIPC for up to USD500,000.
